div.p: To download geocaches, check the box to the left of each listing you wish to download. When you're done, click the download button to the right. Read about waypoint downloads.

ul.li: If you see an icon next to the cache type graphic, there may be a Trackable Item in the cache. Hover over icons to see additional information. About Trackable Items

Some geocache characteristics make it more likely that a new geocacher will be successful when they are first getting started. Beginner caches incorporate these characteristics:

  • Traditional type
  • Low difficulty
  • Recently found by others
  • No micro sized caches
  • No problems reported
